reviews.review_text:
great show, great era Slightly short show for this era; check out a month later in NYC - about 30 songs a night.

When the sound is working, the mix is pretty good. But there are too many drop offs for downloading. Even if the sound were perfect, it couldn't get five stars - Pigpen's not there!

Wish you guys wouldn't keep chopping The Other One into four separate songs!
